title: EMAC Workshop - Register to Attend
content:
Hello Exoplaneteers!

Register now to attend our upcoming virtural workshop! With over 40 speakers, the EMAC workshop will showcase a variety of publicly-available resources created by the exoplanet community.

View the schedule or submit the registration form. We hope to see you there!

Happy Exploring!
tweet_content:
Register now to attend the #EMAC workshop!

View the schedule and register on our website: https://emac.gsfc.nasa.gov/workshop/
